{"tid":1480238,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【珍芳達悼念亡弟】《迷幻車手》彼得方達 (Peter Fonda) 病逝，享年79歲","createTime":"2019-08-17T08:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T10:17:14.000Z","uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d332f1b49f89d718e2075d6cc58e23bfab4cde5d","tid":1480238,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190817/s00009/2c8fd69a9dfdf43617d79712ee5eee02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190817%2Fs00009%2F2c8fd69a9dfdf43617d79712ee5eee02.jpg&h=e173ec7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷李活經典電影《迷幻車手》(Easy Rider) 男星彼得方達（Peter Fonda）昨日因肺癌導致呼吸衰竭，於洛杉磯家中病逝，享年79歲。他的胞姊兼金像影后珍芳達（Jane Fonda）發表聲明悼念：「我很傷心，彼得是我最疼惜的乖弟弟，過去數日我們共度了美好的時光，他是笑着離開的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pmcvariety.files.wordpress.com/2014/07/unadjustednonraw_thumb_f37.jpeg?w=997\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpmcvariety.files.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F07%2Funadjustednonraw_thumb_f37.jpeg%3Fw%3D997&h=a802a07a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/4/4f/Ulees_gold.jpg/250px-Ulees_gold.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2F4%2F4f%2FUlees_gold.jpg%2F250px-Ulees_gold.jpg&h=cfeb3170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1940年生於紐約的彼得方達，從影超過50年，代表作包括獲提名奧斯卡最佳劇本的《迷幻車手》，並憑《Ulee's Gold》奪得金球獎影帝。他的父親是《十二怒漢》(12 Angry Men) 男星亨利方達（Henry Fonda），女兒是《墮落花》(La Femme Nikita) 碧姬芳達（Bridget Fonda）。2011年6月，彼得跟女友Margaret &quot;Parky&quot; DeVogelaere在夏威夷舉行婚禮，成為他的第3任妻子。彼得臨終前，家人一直陪伴在側。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2019/08/1862/1048/GettyImages-166988108.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa57.foxnews.com%2Fstatic.foxnews.com%2Ffoxnews.com%2Fcontent%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F1862%2F1048%2FGettyImages-166988108.jpg%3Fve%3D1%26tl%3D1&h=bb3e057e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左起：彼得方達、亨利方達、珍方達，1963年。<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190817/1566019957491/【珍芳達悼念亡弟】《迷幻車手》彼得方達病逝-享年79歲\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190817%2F1566019957491%2F%E3%80%90%E7%8F%8D%E8%8A%B3%E9%81%94%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5%E4%BA%A1%E5%BC%9F%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E8%BF%B7%E5%B9%BB%E8%BB%8A%E6%89%8B%E3%80%8B%E5%BD%BC%E5%BE%97%E6%96%B9%E9%81%94%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B479%E6%AD%B2&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmr0p1Vm5vkyQgjvFoLOApLI%3D&h=7c6d4f2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190817%2F1566019957491%2F%E3%80%90%E7%8F%8D%E8%8A%B3%E9%81%94%E6%82%BC%E5%BF%B5%E4%BA%A1%E5%BC%9F%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E8%BF%B7%E5%B9%BB%E8%BB%8A%E6%89%8B%E3%80%8B%E5%BD%BC%E5%BE%97%E6%96%B9%E9%81%94%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E4%BA%AB%E5%B9%B479%E6%AD%B2&h=2a531806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190817/1566019957491/【珍芳達悼念亡弟】《迷幻車手》彼得方達病逝-享年79歲</a>"},{"pid":"49ebf18bb86ededb32f4357a5dbfb000d1fb416e","tid":1480238,"uid":153600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:24:11.000Z","msg":"記得佢配過gta sa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0903f70d67d59eb838f82a2445a6ef256ac61781","tid":1480238,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49ebf18bb86ededb32f4357a5dbfb000d1fb416e","tid":1480238,"uid":153600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:24:11.000Z","msg":"記得佢配過gta sa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估唔到會有人留言 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi